Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}星塵似烈陽如火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:45.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}雖然耀眼 但是也看得見陰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:48.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}迷惑內心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:50.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}漫天飄零的火星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:54.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm me, my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}生而為人何所為?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:01:00.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}舉世人生當何為?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:02.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}腳下之地何處是?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:59.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}無止境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:02.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}福地洞天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:06.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}世界從來都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:08.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}一遍遍地自我說服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:11.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}以為自己早已看清
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:12.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}思念在流轉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:15.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}雖仍有迷茫 但我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:20.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}彷徨於時空的迷途者
